Cobbled together potato soup recipe that hit the mark. The twins were a little over five months old when we first made this.

1/3 bag of gold potatoes
4 cups broth made with bouillon (2 cubes)
Milk? 2 cups?
Cook potatoes until falling apart. Smash up a little with an immersion blender.


